= section "The Present Tense" do
  = section "Regular Forms" do
    %p The following table shows the regular present-tense forms in each of the four conjugations. The verbs shown are <i>levá</i> “wash”, <i>debé</i> “need”, <i>vèndey</i> “sell”, and <i>chenoschí</i> “recognize”.
